channel.title: Just a Small Thanks
channel.description:
As much as it pains me to say it without this website and moparscape are what got me to where I am today in terms of my career and how much I actually know when it comes to programming, computer hardware, computer software, networking etc...
At the age of 19 I'm a software developer for a fairly large company creating automotive software on £20k/year with no actual programming/comp-sci qualifications whatsoever and it's all because of this place :rolleyes:
